{"tid":110352,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"呢塊膠紙好特別　　網民個個都瘋傳","createTime":"2017-02-06T15:09:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T05:17:48.000Z","uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b5d36355bf85a7e81d6533b3e13470651158b306","tid":110352,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:09:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/flex-tape.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2Fflex-tape.jpg&h=06facfd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算身在香港，大家有時都會遇到不同物件漏水的情況。最近網上就有一個膠紙廣告，獲不少網民瘋傳。當中售賣的產品，可以貼在漏水的表面，而且非常堅固，最誇張的是最後的部份⋯<br />\n<br />\n片：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0xzN6FM5x_E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0xzN6FM5x_E&d=%2FAErJKvlI7yUl6Jkpxfv8DQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=ce361406\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0xzN6FM5x_E</a><br />\n<br />\n在影片的最後部份，主持人把船切開一半，然後再用上其產品貼好，繼續可以正常使用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。雖然以雙面方式去貼，但由此可看到其產品的強勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"afb354792d841b0d64e2f343242e80e87d4a3665","tid":110352,"uid":675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:13:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf6f8a2e3244896e7f4b5abcad5f18c40f07957","tid":110352,"uid":4997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:15:02.000Z","msg":"我都睇過 但好似有啲伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03b98e811b89082eff715dc368355ae965686dde"